Source: jsonschema
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/theory/pg-jsonschema-boon

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-jsonschema
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-jsonschema
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: JSON Schema validation functions for PostgreSQL
 jsonschema provides JSON Schema validation functions for PostgreSQL using the
 Boon validator. This is the theory/pg-jsonschema-boon extension, not the
 Supabase pg_jsonschema extension.
